## ⚙️ Hardware Requirements
| Component           |                      Description |
|---------------------|----------------------------------|
| Arduino Uno         | Main microcontroller             |
| Potentiometers (x2) | Volume and brightness control    |
| Joystick module     | Mouse movement and click         |
| SG90 Servo Motor    | RAM usage indicator              |
| LEDs (x4)           | CPU temperature indicator        |
| Jumper wires        | Connections                      |
| Breadboard          | Circuit setup                    |

